Traineeship Description:
This position reports to the Director and Senior Associate and works together with all colleagues. Dr Biz Pte Ltd is a professional firm that provides all accounting related services (except Audit), we expect our employees to be independent and able to learn at a fast and on job environment.

Trainee to be involved in:
1. Preparation of accounts
2. Preparation of payroll
3. Preparation of financial statements
4. Preparation for tax computation
5. Other duties in connection with the accounting profession

Skill and competencies trainee will learn:
1. Application of knowledge of accounts into real business
2. Bookkeeping of different industries
3. Financial statement preparation
4. Tax computation preparation
5. Preparation of corporate secretarial documents

Minimum Qualification: Bachelor's Degree

Eligibility Criteria for SGUnitedTraineeships:
•Singapore Citizen or Permanent Resident; and
a.Graduated or graduating in calendar year 2019 or 2020 from universities, or other educational institutions (e.g. private universities and overseas institutions); or
b.Graduated earlier from above institutions and completed National Service in 2019 or 2020.